{"tid":1524531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民對香港警察宣言","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:30:58.000Z","uid":226471,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"45091d695580f1e9c36ccb9abe6b63642deb55a8","tid":1524531,"uid":226471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:28:50.000Z","msg":"只要此時 自由還比生命昂貴<br />\n不論天涯海角<br />\n還有一個為自由而呼吸的香港人<br />\n你們就妄想有安穩的生活<br />\n煙和火即使為人民的葬禮加上幾分顏色<br />\n也將及不上你們的滿手血腥的艷眼<br />\n<br />\n人民不會忘記 亦未敢忘記<br />\n怕成了你們手中惡臭的分享者<br />\n<br />\n終有一日 自由會便宜下來<br />\n你們將會被人民清算<br />\n高貴的鮮血所換來的<br />\n你們將不能分羹<br />\n換來的只有比死更痛苦的折磨<br />\n死刑 將會是一種求之不得的禮物<br />\n<br />\n所以 你們繼續你們的尋歡吧<br />\n繼續氣勢蕩蕩的屠殺吧<br />\n曱甴們將在勝利的一方共候你們<br />\n我們 是殺不盡的"},{"pid":"a833e632ec3352dfbb3ec40c0a12411a81e842d8","tid":1524531,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:29:18.000Z","msg":"［文宣超新星爆炸］ 魔警阻止人道救援<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMjHJNz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMjHJNz.jpg&h=3027d600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/125201912155933?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F110776013598523%2Fposts%2F125201912155933%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70rXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=ae006954\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/125201912155933?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n好撚唔人道 係咪可以推到班撚樣上軍事法庭<br />\nSorry P牌每日一post 有冇手足幫手開post"},{"pid":"10bf2d5759188c8bafbcdbe324a60c66ee2d7fc4","tid":1524531,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:29:27.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lz7uo3t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLz7uo3t.jpg&h=4ed7d51c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />